_Hif’il_ Ongoing Participle:
The [[{{_Hif’il_}} binyan]] has an [[{{ongoing participle}} form]], which is one of the [[Hif’il Forms|forms of the _hif’il_ binyan]].
- The _hif’il_ ongoing participle has [[_Hif’il_ ongoing participle for regular shorushim|conjugations for regular shorushim]].
- The _hif’il_ ongoing participle has conjugations for irregular shorushim which will be added at a later time.
